==> Branching:-
--> A branch is a part of main repo where multiple dev. work on diff features of the same project.

 5 types of branches:-
 * main/master branch
 * features branch
 * Release branch
 * Develop branch
 * hotfix branch

==> main/master branch:- A branch which production code is available.
==> features branch:- A branch is a place where multiple developer can work on a single branch, so each dev. work on 1 feautres branch.
==> Release branch:- A branch user to fixed the bugs without release the production.
==> Develop branch:- A branch is user to combine 2 diff branches code into a single branch to test the code & integration.
==> hotfix branch :- fixing the bug in the production.

