==> Rebase:-
--> rebase is alternate for merge which will not create any merge commits will merging the branches.
--> It follows a linear format of commit history.(Single line commit from top to bottom).
     A -- B -- C -- F -- d -- E
--> Rebase maintain clean commit history.
